    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Catfall</strong>, you are the most precious member of a spaceship crew — a cat whose warmth and gentle purrs bring comfort to everyone on board. Life is perfect… until a sudden disaster throws everything into chaos. And who knows — maybe now the fate of the entire crew will be up to one small, fluffy hero…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s all in your paws! Embark on a short <i>sci-fi cat adventure</i> and save the ship… or at least try not to make things worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/ab8f6f0d9ec2698e46815e97d8350ef7.poster.avif?t=1763466491\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/ab8f6f0d9ec2698e46815e97d8350ef7.webm?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/ab8f6f0d9ec2698e46815e97d8350ef7.mp4?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE SPACESHIP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire starship is at your service now, and you are the master here! Sneak into hidden corners, uncover the crew’s secrets and go everywhere you can stick your little nose.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE A CAT AND HAVE FUN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t forget to be your adorable feline self — hunt for snacks, claim the coziest nap spots, and keep your spirits high. After all, your well-being might just be the key to surviving this journey. And remember: naughtiness is always an option.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/1461030d9cfa3d3d3f0aa1b4a1427c88.poster.avif?t=1763466491\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/1461030d9cfa3d3d3f0aa1b4a1427c88.webm?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/1461030d9cfa3d3d3f0aa1b4a1427c88.mp4?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a cat, you’re surprisingly good at solving various puzzles. Push a button here, drag a cable there, and suddenly — the power’s back on! Maybe it’s just feline curiosity at work, but  does it matter if it works.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERCOME DANGERS AND SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun is fine, but don’t forget the disaster. A kitty probably can’t repair a high-tech starship, but you’ll still be invaluable to your crew. Use your agility and quiet sneaking to help the mission. Most importantly — keep track of how many lives you have left, and don’t forget to land on your paws!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/19a53a1d0d12578e2806f1d3c3dca9f6.poster.avif?t=1763466491\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/19a53a1d0d12578e2806f1d3c3dca9f6.webm?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/19a53a1d0d12578e2806f1d3c3dca9f6.mp4?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR CAT </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, you can choose which one you want to play: an orange troublemaker, a calm grey homebody, a white handsome dust collector, or this black ball of fur with green eyes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/b09e667cf883a6bec511d41b6bec641c.poster.avif?t=1763466491\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/b09e667cf883a6bec511d41b6bec641c.webm?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325350/extras/b09e667cf883a6bec511d41b6bec641c.mp4?t=1763466491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
